Construction de la carte¶

folium.Choropleth(
 geo_data=etat,
 name='Mortalite',
 data=donne_mort,
 columns=['Province_State', 'Ratio'],
 key_on='feature.properties.name',
 fill_opacity=0.7,
 line_opacity=0.2,
 fill_color='YlOrRd',
 legend_name='Repartition de la mortalite',
).add_to(m)

Commentaires :¶
